{"tid":1533337,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［睇全文］為中六同學補下化學知識","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:20:59.000Z","uid":316034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d74403c898c732f9ef5e58a689e72c436c9d170f","tid":1533337,"uid":316034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"各位中六同學，相信大家都因為黎緊嘅DSE而好緊張啦！所以小弟就打翻啲野比大家溫溫書啦！小弟Chem好啲所以就首先係preparation of water soluble salts!<br />\n<br />\n要準備water soluble salts 好簡單㗎啫！以著名嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肥料／炸藥，硝酸銨</span></span> (Ammonium Nitrate, NH4NO3)為例。步驟十分簡單！<br />\n<br />\n1. 將所需分量嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">硝酸</span></span> (Nitric Acid, HNO3，五金鋪話要<span style=\"color: blue;\">硝漒</span>就好似有) 倒落一個玻璃量杯度。（記住係玻璃啊！金屬可能會有反應！）<br />\n2. 跟住，將相應分量嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">氨水</span></span>（Aqueous Ammonia, NH3(aq)，洗窗水就係）慢慢倒落去。   （如果唔知點計要倒幾多，就搵pH paper度pH，倒到變中性就得。DSE唔recommend）<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">硝酸</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">氨水</span></span>會有中和反應（neutralization）出黎就得翻<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">硝酸銨</span></span>同水，要得到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">硝酸銨粉</span></span>，只需慢慢煮到乾水就得。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>硝酸銨只要唔係同糖、鋁粉等混合就唔驚爆炸嘅！</strong></span></span>（當然唔好太大火）<br />\n4. 最後只需要用紙巾印乾或者曬乾就有可以用嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">硝酸銨</span></span>啦！（無呢個step其實無所謂，不過DSE好似會扣分）<br />\n<br />\n以上只係例子，但其他嘅water soluble salts，例如食鹽（Sodium Chloride, NaCl）都可以用同樣方式製造。只需要將硝酸同氨水換造對應嘅酸同鹼就得！<br />\n<br />\n記住化學雖有趣但係都要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">注意安全</span></span>啊！<br />\n<br />\nDSE加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faab3dc61476657fe6106246191db5325cf323f6","tid":1533337,"uid":316034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:56:44.000Z","msg":"Push俾各位中六同學睇啦！"},{"pid":"099458728f79da4760fac6a7fdc5d06fad3788b3","tid":1533337,"uid":316034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"37b07e21a9b5affa1b347aee0890493498b7f811","tid":1533337,"uid":316034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f90f13af57a6287e677c27405c4ebfd9bb99381d","tid":1533337,"uid":316034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"DSE好仲要㗎！"},{"pid":"bdc8e25fb9e13ef60b0ec9a2287a64c00aa800f9","tid":1533337,"uid":316034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"各位要Chem攞5**。有咩化學仲想知都可以答吓㗎！"},{"pid":"99c2d6c050849cecc65d8c5b5f5889d4c8c03017","tid":1533337,"uid":271088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"Dse 同學加油"}]}